Analyzer Feedback from IntelliJ

## Version information

- `IDEA IC-191.7479.19`
- `2.4.0`
- `IC-191.7479.19, JRE 1.8.0_202-release-1483-b58x64 JetBrains s.r.o, OS Mac OS X(x86_64) v10.14.5, screens 2560x1440  Retina`
Please file this bug report at https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/new.

---

## What happened

Nothing but create a new project.

## Version information

IntelliJ IDEA `2019.1.3` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 37.1.3` • Dart plugin `191.7830`

Flutter 1.7.8+hotfix.4 • channel beta • https://github.com/flutter/flutter.git
Framework • revision 20e59316b8 (5 days ago) • 2019-07-18 20:04:33 -0700
Engine • revision fee001c93f
Tools • Dart 2.4.0

## Exception
